  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, observational clinical multicentric study in ICU; during the period surrounding
      the orotracheal intubation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Main objective: to describe the characteristics of reventilation collapse: collapse rate,
      duration and treatment implemented

      Secondary objectives:

        -  identify risk factors of reventilation collapse

        -  compare mortality, hemodynamic, respiratory, infectious and biological data between
           collapse group and no reventilation collapse group.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
